    "The cost functional is of the form",
    "The study of these types of problems is motivated by control problems where the particles are modeled by infinite-dimensional dynamics belonging to some of the most prominent and wideranging families of stochastic systems, including:",
    "• stochastic partial differential equations (SPDEs),",
    "• path-dependent stochastic differential equations (e.g.",
    "stochastic delay differential equations (SDDEs) or stochastic Volterra integral equations (SVIEs)), • partially observed stochastic systems, leading to control of Zakai-type SPDEs."
